## Component Details

### MainTabNavigation.vue

The MainTabNavigation component provides top-level navigation between personal and community content.

**Properties:**
- `activeTab` (String): Currently active tab ("your-rankings" or "community")

**Events:**
- `@tabChange`: Emitted when a tab is tapped, includes the new active tab

**Implementation Notes:**
- Clear visual distinction between tabs with touch targets sized for fingertip interaction
- Maintains state when navigating between songs
- Accessible touch navigation

### SongCard.vue

The SongCard component displays a compact view of a song in the user's rankings.

**Properties:**
- `songId` (String): Unique identifier for the song
- `title` (String): Name of the song
- `rank` (Number): Position in the user's rankings (null for unranked songs)
- `rating` (Number): User's rating from 1-5 (null if not rated)
- `commentCount` (Number): Number of comments by the user for this song

**Events:**
- `@tap`: Emitted when the card is tapped to view details

**Implementation Notes:**
- Entire card is tappable for better usability on touchscreens
- Clear visual indication of rank and rating
- Compact design optimized for mobile screens

### CommunityTabNavigation.vue

The CommunityTabNavigation component provides nested navigation within the Community tab.

**Properties:**
- `activeTab` (String): Currently active tab ("reviews" or "comments")

**Events:**
- `@tabChange`: Emitted when a tab is tapped, includes the new active tab

**Implementation Notes:**
- Visually distinct from main tab navigation
- Only visible when Community tab is active
- Touch targets sized appropriately for mobile interaction

### ReviewDisplay.vue

The ReviewDisplay component shows the user's review and rating for a song.

**Properties:**
- `songId` (String): ID of the song being reviewed
- `rating` (Number): Current rating value (1-5)
- `review` (String): Current review text
- `lastUpdated` (Date): Timestamp of the last update
- `readOnly` (Boolean): Whether the form is in read-only mode
- `hasReview` (Boolean): Whether the user has created a review

**Events:**
- `@edit`: Emitted when the Edit Review button is tapped
- `@save`: Emitted when a review is saved, includes the rating and review text
- `@share`: Emitted when the Share Review button is tapped

**Implementation Notes:**
- Star rating input with touch-friendly targets
- Character-limited text area with mobile-optimized keyboard
- Clear timestamp of last update
- Touch-friendly UI elements sized for fingertip interaction

### ReviewHistory.vue

The ReviewHistory component displays previous versions of a review.

**Properties:**
- `historyEntries` (Array): List of historical review entries with timestamps and content
- `currentIndex` (Number): Index of the currently displayed review

**Events:**
- `@selectVersion`: Emitted when a historical version is tapped for viewing

**Implementation Notes:**
- Touch-friendly horizontal swipe interface for browsing history
- Clear date indicators for each version
- Visual indication of currently selected version
- Gesture support for swiping between versions

### CommentSection.vue

The CommentSection component manages the user's sequential comments for a song.

**Properties:**
- `songId` (String): ID of the song being commented on
- `comments` (Array): List of user comments with timestamps and content
- `totalUserComments` (Number): Total number of comments by the current user

**Events:**
- `@add`: Emitted when a new comment is added via the mobile input
- `@delete`: Emitted when a comment is deleted via swipe or tap action
- `@edit`: Emitted when a comment is edited after tap-to-edit

**Implementation Notes:**
- Chronological display of comments with newest first
- Mobile-optimized text input with predictive text support
- Clear timestamps for each comment
- Swipe gestures for quick actions on comments

### CommunityReviewsList.vue

The CommunityReviewsList component displays reviews from other users.

**Properties:**
- `songId` (String): ID of the song
- `reviews` (Array): List of community reviews with user info, ratings, and content
- `sortOption` (String): Current sort option ("newest", "highest-rated", etc.)

**Events:**
- `@sortChange`: Emitted when sort option changes via touch selection
- `@loadMore`: Emitted when user taps to load more reviews or swipes up at the bottom of the list

**Implementation Notes:**
- Paginated display with infinite scroll support for mobile
- Touch-friendly sort controls with dropdown selection
- Clear attribution of reviews to users
- Optimized for vertical scrolling on mobile screens

### CommunityCommentsList.vue

The CommunityCommentsList component displays comments from other users.

**Properties:**
- `songId` (String): ID of the song
- `comments` (Array): List of community comments with user info and content
- `sortOption` (String): Current sort option ("newest", "oldest", etc.)

**Events:**
- `@sortChange`: Emitted when sort option changes via touch selection
- `@loadMore`: Emitted when user taps to load more comments or swipes up at the bottom of the list

**Implementation Notes:**
- Paginated display with infinite scroll support for mobile
- Touch-friendly sort controls with dropdown selection
- Clear attribution of comments to users with timestamps
- Optimized for vertical scrolling on mobile screens

### MetricDisplay.vue

The MetricDisplay component shows statistics about reviews and comments.

**Properties:**
- `songId` (String): ID of the song
- `totalReviewers` (Number): Number of users who have reviewed this song
- `totalCommenters` (Number): Number of users who have commented on this song
- `totalComments` (Number): Total number of comments across all users

**Implementation Notes:**
- Compact display of key metrics optimized for mobile screen space
- Used in both personal and community views for context
- Updates in real-time as data changes
- Touch-friendly design with appropriate spacing for mobile viewing

# Edit Rankings View

The Edit Rankings View provides an interface for users to select and rank items within specific music eras, with two distinct ranking modes and enhanced sorting options.

## Screen Overview

**Purpose:** Allow users to select favorite songs from eras and arrange them in a personalized ranking order, with options for quick ranking or full ranking

**Primary Components:**


-   RankingModeSelector.vue (toggle between Quick Rank and Full Rank modes)
-   SelectionTabs.vue (tab navigation between eras)
-   SortingControls.vue (options for sorting songs)
-   ItemChip.vue (multiple instances for selectable songs)
-   HeaderControls.vue (cancel/save buttons, title)
-   SelectionCounter.vue (shows progress)

## Visual Layout

